= Introduction =

vlems - Virtual LEMS
"Your own system administrator"

Currently works only for Ubuntu Hardy. 

= Installation =

Open a terminal and do the following commands:

1. sudo apt-get install cfengine2 git-core
2. git clone http://git.kiskeyix.org/git/vlems
3. sudo cp vlems/inputs/* /etc/cfengine/
4. sudo /usr/sbin/cfagent -qv

From then on the system will maintain itself.
